'''Dilemma''' is an '''Diplomacy''' card for [[Rook]]. It deals 1-6 base damage for four actions, and costs 1 less action every time you '''Gamble''' until the end of your turn. '''Dilemma''' is part of the Gambler and Fixated card set.

After accruing 3 experience '''Dilemma''' upgrades to be "Pale" costing 3 actions, or to be "Boosted" dealing 1-8 base damage.